00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:03,110
If he marries a city woman,

904
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:05,030
his life will change.

905
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,110
I've met Zhao Kai.

906
00:37:07,630 --> 00:37:08,510
How old is he?

907
00:37:08,670 --> 00:37:10,000
Seventeen, almost 18.

908
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:10,920
His real age.

909
00:37:14,630 --> 00:37:17,150
His ID says 15.

910
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:18,110
But he's tall.

911
00:37:18,320 --> 00:37:18,960
Everyone would

912
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:19,920
believe he's 18.

913
00:37:20,230 --> 00:37:21,760
Do you know what the requirements are

914
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:22,400
for factory jobs?

915
00:37:22,510 --> 00:37:23,960
What requirements?

916
00:37:24,230 --> 00:37:25,190
It's just a matter

917
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:26,150
of Mr. Meng's word.

918
00:37:30,550 --> 00:37:31,760
Your steamed buns.

919
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:32,400
Enjoy.

920
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,760
This bun isn't wrapped properly.

921
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:44,150
It's still cracked.

922
00:37:44,590 --> 00:37:45,760
He Xiaoju, let me tell you,

923
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,510
the requirements

924
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:48,880
for state-owned factories

925
00:37:49,550 --> 00:37:51,400
are that you be over 18 years old

926
00:37:51,670 --> 00:37:52,880
and a recent high school graduate.

927
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:54,630
Better positions require
a college diploma.

928
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,320
Your son is only 15.

929
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,110
Has he finished high school?

930
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:01,840
Wanzhi, don't be angry.

931
00:38:07,590 --> 00:38:08,760
Zhao Kai doesn't

932
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:11,800
like studying.

933
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:12,360
So...

934
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:13,280
He didn't go to high school.

935
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,480
But we

936
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:17,840
have you.

937
00:38:18,030 --> 00:38:19,190
You're his aunt.

938
00:38:19,670 --> 00:38:21,150
Please help

939
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:22,710
your nephew.

940
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:23,480
I promise

941
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:24,920
that once you've done this,

942
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:25,550
I'll never

943
00:38:25,670 --> 00:38:26,710
bother you again.

944
00:38:27,190 --> 00:38:27,800
Trust me.

945
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,000
I've severed ties

946
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,880
with Mr. Meng.

947
00:38:30,030 --> 00:38:31,030
He's not my family.

948
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:32,280
We don't contact each other.

949
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,320
But He Xiaoju, I have to remind you,

950
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:37,920
you also have

951
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:39,320
a daughter.

952
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:40,590
Her name is Zhao Jun.

953
00:38:41,030 --> 00:38:42,320
Do you know where she is now?

954
00:38:43,550 --> 00:38:44,880
Where could she be?

955
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:47,230
Working in Yu County,

956
00:38:47,550 --> 00:38:48,190
I guess.

957
00:38:48,710 --> 00:38:49,360
I'm telling you,

958
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:50,670
I've worried myself

959
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:52,400
sick over her.

960
00:38:52,630 --> 00:38:53,480
She made my life harder.

961
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,280
I arranged such

962
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:55,480
a great marriage for her.

963
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,480
Yet she refused.

964
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,000
The wedding money given to her

965
00:38:59,230 --> 00:39:00,230
was returned.

966
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:02,320
What kind of mother are you?

967
00:39:02,710 --> 00:39:03,960
You're a complete jerk.

968
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:06,150
Do you know how old he is?

969
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:07,070
You brought him

970
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,670
all the way to Shenzhen

971
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:10,840
just to plead for you, right?

972
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:13,110
Yes.

973
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,510
For my sake...

974
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:15,150
Shut up!

975
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:18,960
Finish your food and get out of here.

976
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,440
Send him back the way

977
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:21,550
you brought him.

978
00:39:25,150 --> 00:39:25,670
Check, please.

979
00:39:26,110 --> 00:39:26,960
This way please.

980
00:39:33,150 --> 00:39:34,280
All you know is eating.

981
00:39:42,070 --> 00:39:43,150
Why are you up so early today?

982
00:39:45,760 --> 00:39:47,280
I wonder if they're back yet.

983
00:39:48,150 --> 00:39:49,000
What if they didn't

984
00:39:49,150 --> 00:39:50,230
bring enough money?

985
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:51,670
Ah.

986
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:53,590
You were so angry yesterday,

987
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:54,920
and you regret it already.

988
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,070
They are, after all, my...

989
00:40:02,510 --> 00:40:03,670
They came all the way here,

990
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:06,280
and I only treated them to breakfast.

991
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,070
Was I bad?

992
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:10,880
They crossed the line first.

993
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,400
Mr. Meng is an honest man.

994
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:13,440
How could he break

995
00:40:13,480 --> 00:40:14,440
his principles for them?

996
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,800
I wasn't just angry about that.

997
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,670
I felt sorry for Zhao Jun.

998
00:40:19,320 --> 00:40:20,320
He Xiaoju had no idea

999
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,110
she is in Shenzhen,

1000
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,840
nor did she care what she is doing.

1001
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:25,440
No wonder Zhao Jun is so introverted.

1002
00:40:25,710 --> 00:40:27,280
She endures all the bullying.

1003
00:40:28,150 --> 00:40:29,070
No one cares for her at home.

1004
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:30,440
She's weak facing people.

1005
00:40:33,190 --> 00:40:34,360
I'll have to go see Zhao Jun.

1006
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:35,360
I'm worried

1007
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,800
about her being bullied

1008
00:40:37,230 --> 00:40:38,440
by Nan if she stays there.

1009
00:40:39,110 --> 00:40:40,590
You're such a worrywart.

1010
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:42,360
One, two, go!

1011
00:40:44,510 --> 00:40:45,630
One, two.

1012
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:52,440
What's wrong?

1013
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:53,440
What's wrong?

1014
00:40:59,670 --> 00:41:00,800
What are you doing here?

1015
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:11,320
Why are you doing this?

1016
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:13,880
How can I do

1017
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,110
business with you here?

1018
00:41:17,550 --> 00:41:18,880
What Xiaoju asked

1019
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:20,880
isn't difficult for you.

1020
00:41:21,110 --> 00:41:22,550
Just help her.

1021
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:23,800
You blackmailing me?

1022
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,150
I'm begging you.

1023
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:26,480
What if I don't help?

1024
00:41:26,590 --> 00:41:27,000
Then I'll

1025
00:41:28,150 --> 00:41:29,320
just stay here

1026
00:41:29,510 --> 00:41:30,360
and not leave.

1027
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:31,920
Get up!

1028
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,320
Mr. He,

1029
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:34,670
please get up.

1030
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,630
We can talk things over.

1031
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,360
No need.

1032
00:41:41,590 --> 00:41:42,360
He wants to stay,

1033
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,190
then let him stay.

1034
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:43,880
Come.

1035
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:44,800
We're closed today.

1036
00:41:45,110 --> 00:41:45,630
I'll go sleep.

1037
00:41:45,630 --> 00:41:46,030
Hey.

1038
00:41:46,150 --> 00:41:46,800
I'm going home.

1039
00:41:47,030 --> 00:41:48,280
What are you doing?

1040
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:49,000
Coming or not?

1041
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,590
If you don't, I'll fire you.

1042
00:41:53,280 --> 00:41:54,110
Wanzhi, you...

1043
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:03,320
Juan.

1044
00:42:04,670 --> 00:42:06,110
What does she mean?

1045
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,550
She's going to fire you?

1046
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:10,630
Mr. He,

1047
00:42:11,280 --> 00:42:12,150
I don't dare talk

1048
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:13,400
to you anymore.

1049
00:42:13,710 --> 00:42:14,760
Listen to me,

1050
00:42:15,230 --> 00:42:16,400
just leave.

1051
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:18,190
Wanzhi can ignore you.

1052
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:19,360
But the market supervisors

1053
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:19,880
aren't polite.

1054
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:21,320
They might call the police.

1055
00:42:21,590 --> 00:42:23,400
I'm her dad.

1056
00:42:24,030 --> 00:42:26,150
I'm not afraid of the police.

1057
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:31,440
Juan.

1058
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:31,960
Juan.

1059
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:32,960
Juan.

1060
00:42:33,190 --> 00:42:34,710
You're my sister's friend.

1061
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,360
So I'm practically your sister too.

1062
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:37,320
Xiaoju.

1063
00:42:38,280 --> 00:42:39,800
I work for her.

1064
00:42:44,230 --> 00:42:46,190
Then go tell your boss.
